StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetCurrentFyVisitRecapInfo]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@Organiza.onId int, @SchoolCode int, @FiscalYear int AS BEGIN
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
SELECT [CurrentFyVisitRecapId] ,[Organiza.onId] ,[Appointments] ,[Contacts] ,[Interviews] ,[Nwas] ,[Date] ,[Purpose] ,[School_Code] AS SchoolCode ,[FiscalYear] ,[LastUpdateUserId] FROM [MCRISS].[USMC].[CurrentFYVisitRecap]
WHERE Organiza.onId = @Organiza.onId and School_Code = @SchoolCode and FiscalYear = @FiscalYear
END
